Questions
Which tool can copy blobs from one Azure Storage container to another container programmatically,
and delete data from the source container once the copy is complete?

Ans - Microsoft Azure Storage Data Movement Library

LRS: 3 copies in a single data center within a single region.
ZRS: 3 copies across three availability zones within a single region.
GZRS: 6 copies, with 3 copies in one region (across three zones) and 3 additional copies in a secondary region (across three zones).

